    "description": "JIG-SAW INC., a software technology company, provides IoT data control services in Japan. It offers auto sensing and auto control technology platform and services; end-to-end automatic data control services; and big data, cloud, servers, networks, various applications, various platforms, security software, IoT devices, communication modules, various equipment, devices, cells, organisms, etc. The company also provides secure data control and interactive control services on the mobile edge computing (MEC) platform; research and development of autonomous driving software, next-generation real-time OS, next-generation modules, etc.; direct control of cells and organisms using software; and automation, decentralization, and sharing of all industries based on operation technology (OT). In addition, it offers edge computing, embedded software, and system management services. Further, the company offers NEQTO.ai, IoT-OPS, NEQTO, and puzzle platforms and services. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
